    • org.apache.storm.security.auth.kerberos.AutoTGT

    public class AutoTGT
extends Object
implements IAutoCredentials, ICredentialsRenewer, IMetricsRegistrant

    Automatically take a user’s TGT, and push it, and renew it in Nimbus.
